mpcliffs
========

all-in-one tool to search for and play entries in a the current mpd playlist.


installation
------------
invoke without arguments and you will see something like:

./mpcliffs install [target]: make symlinks in $1 
  or here in: (/home/jaroslav/src/bash/mpcliffs)

so give it a folder where to put the links and it will create symlinks to 
itself.

subcommands
-----------

mpc-whatson		#
mpc-jump
mpc-fade
mpc-wake
mpc-remove
mpc-keep
mpc-cdnp
mpc-symlink
mpc-queue
mpc-pwd-update
mpc-pwd-add
mpc-x [next|prev|%position%]
